Package: lidhandler
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: systemd
Maintainer: Aditya Anil <aditya.anil.productions@gmail.com>
Description: Toggle laptop lid switch suspend behavior via systemd-logind
 LidHandler manages laptop lid switch behavior using systemd-logind drop-in
 configuration files. Prevent suspend-on-lid-close without modifying the
 base logind.conf. Supports enable, disable, status, and toggle commands.
